      • setStatus

        public void setStatus(java.lang.String status)
        Sets the report status, receiving a string parameter which must be "active", "in charge", "in_charge" or "closed". If it is different from these 4 strings (letters' case does not matter) an IllegalArgumentException will be thrown
        Parameters:
        status - the status to set
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the given string status is not valid
